      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a practical choice for someone prioritizing function over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several visible scratches, faded paint on the hood, and a few small dings around the door panels. Inside, the upholstery has some noticeable staining and minor wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it has high mileage and will likely require some routine maintenance\u2014such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up\u2014in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done but is priced to reflect its current cosmetic and mechanical state.",
