      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this absolute stunner. Honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I've babied this car from day one! It\u2019s in truly flawless shape, inside and out, and I'm only letting it go because I need something bigger for the family. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
