      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is an impeccably preserved 2009 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This example features the 3.8L MA1 flat-six engine utilizing Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), producing a robust 385 hp with a linear power band and no IMS bearing concerns. The drivetrain is anchored by the 7-speed Porsche Doppelkupplung (PDK) dual-clutch transmission, offering lightning-fast gear synchronization and optimized torque delivery. Equipped with the Sport Chrono Package Plus and Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), the chassis dynamics remain sharp and communicative, benefiting from the era-defining hydraulic steering rack. The exterior retains its factory-original paint with consistent micron readings, while the interior shows zero evidence of bolster compression or switchgear delamination. A truly turn-key specimen with a comprehensive service dossier, representing the zenith of water-cooled analog performance.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Full service records. New tires. Pristine interior.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
