      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard rarely seen on the secondary market. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, all protected by a recently applied professional ceramic coating. The original alloy wheels are pristine, free of any curb rash or pitting. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a complete service history from authorized dealerships and a smooth, responsive powertrain that feels as tight as the day it left the factory. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this is the one. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a folder of maintenance receipts.",
      "price": 44900.0,
